data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS! A great example of an attached Patio Home in the gated community of Sandoval. Freshly painted and priced to MOVE! Ease of ownership and limited availability make these very desirable, and this one looks and feels brand new! The master and second bedroom — each with their own bathroom — as well as the central den and dining room, make great use of the nearly 1600 square feet of living space. The kitchen is open to the living room and perfect for entertaining friends and family. The HOA dues cover nearly everything for worry-free Florida living. The community of Sandoval — with tennis, pickleball, volleyball, resort style pool, dog parks, clubhouse and MORE — won't disappoint and neither will this home!
